summary:
I‚Äôm a UX professional with a decade of experience aligning business objectives with user needs. I love a good problem. Currently working in Fintech.

Previously, I worked in the travel industry for Travelport Digital, working in both Product and Client teams.

I began my design career in the gambling industry, where human behaviour is at its most irrational and all the rules of design (if there are any) can be thrown straight out the window.

I‚Äôve consistently delivered successful projects across mobile, tablet and desktop and have worked right across the UX design spectrum from User Research to Interaction Design to UI Design.

It‚Äôs pronounced ‚ÄúOwen Oh-Rah-hilly‚Äù :)
